<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>E</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Nunnak Gospel pali chung ah, Fiang tein kan hmuh mi cu
 Pathian nih vawlei a dawt ca, A fapa a kan pek
 Cu fapa nun ngeimi paoh nih, Bawipa sunparnak ding caah
 An nun an pek Bawipa ca an nung cang.

[C1]
   Bawipa nih a herh ah cun, a kan pek cia thluachuah hna hi
   Kal pi ko seh, A sunparnak ding ah cun
   Kan mah ta zei hmanh a um lo, A chaw kengtu lawng kan si e
   Kal pi ko seh, a rak kirthan zau lai.

[V2]
 Jesuh Jeruslem lungrawn, Le chumtual a luh lio ah khan
 Cit bal lomi laa keng cung in, Sunparnak kha a rak hmuh
 A ngeitu nih an tlai kho lo, Bawipa nih a herh hnu ah cun
 A kal pi e, Jeruslem lei ah.

[V3]
 Semnak kan lairam dawh chungin, Nu le Pa seihno vialte hna
 Kan Bawipa ca nai manh cang maw, A tu Bawipa nih an herh
 Kal cang u sih lo thar chungah, Thil pek le thlacamnak te he
 Kan rian a si, Bawipa nih a kan fial.

[V4]
 Hi thawngtha theitu vialte hna, Hi kong hi nan ruat bal maw
 Satan nih a kalpi mi cu, Zeitik hmanh an kir ti lo
 Siseh liannganbik Bawipa nih, A kalpi mi chaw vialte cu
 An kir than e, Let tampi in, an kir e.</lyrics>
<title>NUNNAK GOSPEL PALI</title>
</song>